data.description: active under contract - accepting back up offersWelcome to your dream home at 10451 Ventura Dr, Spring Hill, FL 34608! Priced to sell! This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom pool home is nestled in the heart of Spring Hill, within the highly desirable Seven Hills Estates community. As you step inside this charming residence, you'll discover a host of impressive features that are sure to capture your heart. With new stainless steel appliances installed in 2021, you can embark on culinary adventures in the well-appointed kitchen, where your inner chef will find its haven. The allure of wood laminate floors graces the entire home, providing both a timeless elegance and ease of maintenance.Your outdoor oasis awaits as you make your way to the captivating pool area, thoughtfully enclosed with a screen, allowing you to enjoy the Florida sunshine without any of the pests. The master bathroom is a true retreat with a separate tub and shower, offering relaxation and convenience. Cathedral ceilings elevate the living space, creating an airy and open ambiance.Recent updates include new screens on the lanai in 2022 and a new pool heater in 2021, ensuring that your comfort and enjoyment are top priorities. With these enhancements, you can embrace the Florida lifestyle to the fullest.
